# Task Tracker — Architecture Rules

## Project Stack

- React Native with Expo (managed workflow, new architecture enabled)
- TypeScript strict mode
- NativeWind v4 for styling (Tailwind classes via `className`)
- Context + useReducer for state (no Redux, no Zustand)
- AsyncStorage for local persistence
- expo-router v3+ for file-based navigation
- `@/` path alias resolving to project root

