## Auth Screens

### LoginScreen

File: `screens/login-screen.tsx`

Fields:
- Email (TextInput, keyboardType: email-address)
- Password (TextInput, secureTextEntry)
- "Login" button → calls `login(email, password)` from UserContext → redirects to `/(tabs)`
- "Don't have an account? Sign up" link → `router.push('/(auth)/signup')`

Validation:
- Both fields required (show inline error if empty on submit)
- Email must contain `@`

### SignupScreen

File: `screens/signup-screen.tsx`

Fields:
- Name (TextInput)
- Email (TextInput, keyboardType: email-address)
- Password (TextInput, secureTextEntry)
- "Sign Up" button → calls `signup(name, email, password)` from UserContext → redirects to `/(tabs)`
- "Already have an account? Login" link → `router.push('/(auth)/login')`

Validation:
- All fields required
- Email must contain `@`
- Password minimum 6 characters

Both screens:
- Use the cream `#fffce3` background to match the walkthrough
- Keep consistent button style (dark pill, `#242424`, `rounded-full`)
